  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><strong>Wednesday 2nd Novemeber 2016,</strong> Godalming – Inghams has introduced the new Lakes and Mountains Summer 2017 brochure with s<strong>avings including up to £100 per couple discounts, frozen excursion prices, free bar credit and free or reduced travel in resort</strong>. Inghams have also expanded the programme in Italy adding<strong> 4 new resorts</strong> Como, Lazise, Lake Levico and the Venetian Riviera. Inghams offer over <strong>100 resorts,</strong> cities and tours in Europe with direct flights from <strong>23 regional airport</strong> to <strong>7 countries</strong> and offer flexible durations from <strong>short breaks to longer 14 night holidays</strong>.</p>
<p><br /><strong>Paul Carter, Chief Operating Officer said</strong>: “<em>With the new Lakes and Mountains brochure Inghams have tried to pass on as many savings as possible on to the customers. We know the weakened pound will affect holiday makers and therefore we have frozen the cost of pre-bookable excursions, offer discounts of up to £100 per couple and even offer 15% off at Cotswold outdoors for all Inghams guests.”</em></p>
<p><br /><strong>Features of the 2017 brochure</strong></p>
<p><br /><strong>Savings</strong></p>
<p>• <strong>Inghams double saver plus offers</strong> – this offer is available on selected properties in Austria, France, Italy, Slovenia and Switzerland and all chalet and Chalet Hotels on bookings made by 31.01.17 and is in addition to any other offers. <br />• <strong>Inghams saver plus</strong>- where the £100 saving is not available Inghams offer £50 saving per couple on bookings made by 31.01.17<br />• <strong>Inghams Plus</strong>- this includes free packed lunches, free afternoon tea and cakes, free bike hire, free Berlitz pocket guides and free hotel guided walks and Inghams guided wander walks. <br />• <strong>Excursion prices frozen at preview price</strong><br />• <strong>€100 bar credit in all Chalet Hotels</strong> on bookings made by 31.01.17<br />• <strong>Free or reduced travel in resort</strong>- free use of cable cars, chairlifts and public transport in many resorts, half-price travel throughout Switzerland, free travel throughout Switzerland for children up to 15 years old<br />• <strong>Free guided walks</strong>- these includes Inghams guided wander walks (local walks organised up to 3 times per week by the Inghams Rep or guide, free local tourist office walks (in selected resorts), free hotel guided walks (led by professional guides in many hotels). <br />• <strong>20% off Cicerone Walking Guidebooks</strong></p>
<p><br /><strong>What’s NEW?</strong><br /><strong>4 NEW RESORTS</strong> - Due to popular demand Inghams have expanded their presence in <a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italy</a> adding Como, Lazies, Lake Levico and the Venetian Riviera as well as a NEW Beaches and Lakes dual centre holiday which combines a stay on the Venetian Riviera with one of the Italian Lakes. <br />Sample - 7 nights, 4* Grand Hotel Imperial, Lake Levico, Italy from £799pp, departing May 2017 with return flights and resort transfers (<a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays">www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays</a>, 01483 791 116)</p>
<p><strong>COTSWOLD OUTDOORS</strong> – Inghams guest will receive a 15% discount both instore and online when they make a booking from the Summer 2017 brochure. <br /><strong>NO SINGLE SUPPLEMENT</strong> – Inghams have a selection of hotels where there will be no supplement and sole occupancy rooms in chalets and Chalet Hotels.</p>
<p><br /><strong>Other features</strong><br />A wide selection of accommodation - ranging from hotels, chalets, Chalet Hotels, Inghams all-inclusive packages (including breakfast, lunch and dinner), bed and breakfast, self-catering and exclusive to Inghams properties (ones which are only featured by Inghams in the UK market.</p>
<p><br />Sample - 7 nights, chalet catering (breakfast afternoon tea and a five course evening meal with complimentary wine), 3.5 diamond <a data-udi="umb://document/98e5917964c04bbf9caa7f5e69e9874e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/98e5917964c04bbf9caa7f5e69e9874e}" title="Chalet Hotel Sapinière">Chalet Hotel Sapinière</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf}" title="France">France</a> from £395pp, saving £50pp departing May 2017 with return flights and resort transfers. Also available €100 per couple bar credit on all chalets and Chalet Hotels. (<a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays">www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays</a>, 01483 791 116) Offer valid until 31.01.17</p>
<p><strong>For press enquiries, images or a copy of the brochure please contact</strong><br />PR Assistant, Rachel Gaston, Inghams on 014837 91045 / <a href="mailto:rachel.gaston@inghams.co.uk">rachel.gaston@inghams.co.uk</a><br />Senior PR Account Manager, Daniela Resenterra, 020 7593 1771/<a href="mailto:DanielaR@hillsbalfour.com">DanielaR@hillsbalfour.com</a><br />PR Account Manager, Josie Self, 020 7593 1758/ <a href="mailto:JosieS@hillsbalfour.com">JosieS@hillsbalfour.com</a></p>
<p>ENDS.</p>]]></bodyText>
